definitions.definition: A village in Custer County , Nebraska , United States .
A city , the county seat of Oconto County , Wisconsin , United States , named after the Oconto River.
A town in Oconto County , Wisconsin , United States , partly surrounding the city of the same name.
A river in Wisconsin , United States , the Oconto River , which flows into Green Bay , Lake Michigan .
